{
  "texts": [
    "Choose an actiongoal is a long-term objective, such as maintaining safe and efficient driving.",
    "Each agent first sets its objectives based on the scenario description to inform planning and action decisions.",
    "Make a plan based on the goals: The planning process involves the LLMs devising a strategy that connects identified goals with future actions, ensuring coherent actions over time.",
    "Initially, the LLMs checks for a pre-established plan.",
    "If no such plan exists, the LLMs formulates a new strategy to guide future actions."
  ]
}